==German==
===Etymology===
From German ''[[Vogel]]'' ('[[bird]]') < Proto-Germanic '''*foglaz''' < '''*flug-la-''' ('flyer') < [[PIE]] '''*pleu-''' ('flowing, floating'). Cognate with English [[fowl]].

===Verb===
'''vögeln'''

# to [[mate]] ''(said of birds)''
#''(vulgar)'' to [[fuck]]

